verses.text:
Gone are the doubts that at my heart;
Gone are the fears that held me here;
Gone are the chains that bound me fast;
Jesus has set me free.

Clean is the heart that once was foul;
Clean is the life that once was dark;
Clean is the conscience, free from guilt;
Washed in the cleansing blood.

Now I can go where Jesus led;
Now I can follow where he trod;
Now I can serve him with my all;
Cleansed and made pure.

chorus.text:
Cleansed, cleansed, precious promise,
Cleansed by the blood of the lamb;
White as snow, I am now made;
Cleansed, cleansed, I am.
